				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$9.0106\times {10^{-5}}$$\end{document} at 1000 epochs. In addition, training, validation and testing curves are closed to each other. This means that the designed NN is reliable and can predict its output value efficiently.Figure 10
The performance of the neural network.

